I don’t completely understand the point. Is it suggesting we don’t make rape jokes? I don’t personally find them that funny, but some people do, that’s just how humour works. But to identify someone who finds a rape joke funny next to a rapist isn’t the best comparison. No ones laughing at rape. Rape isn’t funny. The thing that’s funny is abnormality and things you aren’t supposed to say. If I said “there are people in this world who have been physically assaulted by feminists and this page give them a vivid technicolour reliving of perhaps her (by the way you assumed someone who was raped was a female, good one) worst memory” you wouldn’t stop posting. The person being offended is a bi-product of something you’re doing, which I assume is for you to try and make a world a better place. Same applies to people who make insensitive jokes. *mic drop*🥴

I mean if my sense of humor offends u my bad I don’t put rape jokes online in order to be respectful but rape statistics are often exaggerated and are still significantly lower than one would think, I do agree that no rape victims aren’t being sensitive once they’re offended but there’s always gonna be offensive shot out there especially on the internet it’s better to learn to deal with that preach that your supposed to relive the events that transpired and that everyone should stop, people have the right to say whatever they want as they should, and people should get used to it, I’m not saying that those jokes are always in good taste but they are always gonna be around so rather than talk about how terrible they are just ignore them completely this way those who make them don’t get satisfaction, freedom of speech is not suppressed and people don’t get put in a hypersensitive bubble that creates the precedent that if I don’t like what someone says they shouldn’t be saying it

What is so difficult to understand. Making light and playful jests about rape as a "joke" communicates to others that rape is acceptable because its "not a big deal." And if you say "oh but I make rape jokes and I KNOW that rape isn't ok," then you should probably stop making rape jokes because you're contradicting that. Do you have nothing better to joke about?
